START
Input Num1
Input Num2
IF Num1>Num2 THEN
SET Num2 to BINARY and store under the variable B2
SET B2 to 2's complement and store under the variable B22
SET Num1 to binary and store under the B1 variable
Subtraction = B1 + B22
Print Subtraction
ELSE
SET Num1 to binary and set to 2's complement and store under B11 variable
SET Num2 to binary and store under B2 variable
Subtraction = B2 + B11
print Subtraction
END IF
END
